title: Looking Back on Identity with Mars
description:
Mars is a returning guest and good twitter friend of mine, who is also trans. I so appreciate how open he was with my questions, this chat couldn’t have gone any better. He is for sure one of the most chill and cool people I've interviewed, we discuss the past year and the impact it had on his life 
Listen to podcast version here: https://anchor.fm/podcast-9b57fe4/episodes/Looking-Back-on-Identity-with-Mars-ev8k02

Check out his YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCK792gI7-zEik0tB1Ok0l6Q

Follow me on twitter @andrealynnlews
email me at andreawiththebangs@gmail
